You can order Applied Cryptography at your local bookstore.  Here is the
necessary information:

	Title:  APPLIED CRYPTOGRAPAHY: PROTOCOLS, ALGORITHMS AND SOURCE CODE
	Author:  Bruce Schneier
	Publisher:  John Wiley & Sons
	ISBN #:  0-471-5976-2

It will be published in the beginning of November.





